{"id":342740,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/342740","type":2,"name":"Tomorrow's Leaves","name_cn":"","summary":"オリンピズムをテーマにした、8分27秒の手描きアニメーション作品「Tomorrow's Leaves」。同作ではこの地球上のどこかの島を舞台に、突然枯れ始めた平和の証・虹色の葉の謎を解こうと、国も文化も言語も異なる子どもたちが立ち上がり、虹色の葉を宿す「あしたの木」へと旅立つさまが描かれる。制作はオリンピック文化遺産財団と共同で行われ、監督は「火垂るの墓」「かぐや姫の物語」に参加し、スタジオポノックの短編「サムライエッグ」を手がけた百瀬義行が務めた。音楽は「思い出のマーニー」「メアリと魔女の花」の村松崇継が担当している。","eps":[{"id":1044638,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1044638","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"eps_count":1,"air_date":"2021-07-23","air_weekday":5,"images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/76/b0/342740_AF2d5.jpg","common":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/76/b0/342740_AF2d5.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/76/b0/342740_AF2d5.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/s/76/b0/342740_AF2d5.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/76/b0/342740_AF2d5.jpg"},"collection":{"wish":4,"collect":1},"crt":null,"staff":[{"id":1347,"url":"http://bgm.tv/person/1347","name":"百瀬義行","name_cn":"百濑义行","role_name":"","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/0e/55/1347_prsn_anidb.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/0e/55/1347_prsn_anidb.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/0e/55/1347_prsn_anidb.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/0e/55/1347_prsn_anidb.jpg"},"comment":2,"collects":0,"info":{"name_cn":"百濑义行","alias":{"0":"ももせ よしゆき","1":"百瀬ヨシユキ","kana":"ももせよしゆき","romaji":"Momose Yoshiyuki"},"gender":"男","birth":"1953年11月29日"},"jobs":["导演"]},{"id":15336,"url":"http://bgm.tv/person/15336","name":"村松崇継","name_cn":"村松崇继","role_name":"","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/17/73/15336_prsn_mJeSA.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/17/73/15336_prsn_mJeSA.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/17/73/15336_prsn_mJeSA.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/17/73/15336_prsn_mJeSA.jpg"},"comment":1,"collects":0,"info":{"name_cn":"村松崇继","alias":{"kana":"むらまつ たかつぐ","romaji":"muramatsu takatsugu"